
Bloodfist Help:  Toggle

  The toggle command allows you to customize the guild in various ways.
The toggle list command lets you see all of your toggles at once.

  ac   additional commands
       Displays a list of related commands when various guild commands
       are used.

  fs   full score
       Displays the guild info as well as the mud info in the guild score.

  as   auto sheath on retrieve
       When you retrieve a thrown weapon, it can either be moved to the
       inventory or automatically sheathed on your back.

  fm   full monitor
       Whether or not the duration monitor displays the abbreviations
       of the spells names or the full names.

  hm   heartbeat monitor
       Whether or not the duration monitor is displayed during combat.

Usage: toggle <which>
       toggle list

